<h1>How to make Pankcakes</h1>
<h2>By Sheriel Henry</h2>
<p> I like to make pancakes on sunday mornings since I have time to do it, and it is a nice wakeup call. I enjoy addding toppings and different types of fruit to make my pancakes flavorful.</p>
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul>
<li>pancake mix(your choice)</li>
<li>two eggs</li>
<li>vegetable oil</li>
<li>Milk</li>
<li>Butter</li>
<li>Cinninom</li>
<li>fruit</li>
<h4>What to do</h4>
<ol>
<li>crack 2 eggs</li>
<li>Mix pancake mix mix, milk,fruit,and cinninom</li>
<li>heat up frying pan and add butter and oil</li>
<li>when pan is hot add batter to pan and fry it</li>
<li>enjoy!</li>
</ol>
